==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fluorene
<hw>Flu`or*ene</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A colorless, crystalline hydrocarbon, <chform>C13H10</chform>
having a beautiful violet <xex>fluorescence</xex>; whence its name. It
occurs in the higher boiling products of coal tar, and is obtained
artificially.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>fluorescein</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>fluoresceine</ent>⟦br⟧
